{"id":1224,"date":"2025-04-12T00:03:51","date_gmt":"2025-04-11T17:03:51","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?post_type=product&#038;p=1224"},"modified":"2025-11-25T09:38:56","modified_gmt":"2025-11-25T02:38:56","slug":"da-kich-ung-man-do","status":"publish","type":"product","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/da-kich-ung-man-do\/","title":{"rendered":"Da k\u00edch \u1ee9ng m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh t\u1ed1i \u01b0u d\u00e0nh cho da kh\u00f4 r\u00e1p, bong tr\u00f3c, da k\u00edch \u1ee9ng c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu.<\/em><\/p>\n<h3><em>L\u1ee3i \u00edch ch\u00ednh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>C\u1ea5p \u1ea9m, l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da th\u00f4 r\u00e1p, gi\u1ea3m k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/li>\n<li>L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u, lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/li>\n<li>L\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da, k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, da sau n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n.<\/li>\n<li>Da kho\u1ebb m\u1ea1nh, s\u0103n ch\u1eafc, m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng t\u01b0\u01a1i tr\u1ebb h\u1ed3ng h\u00e0o h\u01a1n.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 Oxy Jet v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cung c\u1ea5p oxy tinh khi\u1ebft n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 98%. Khi phun v\u00e0o da \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e2n t\u00e1ch th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1t s\u01b0\u01a1ng Oxy c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng k\u00ednh nm, h\u1ea1t Oxy nguy\u00ean ch\u1ea5t \u0111i s\u00e2u v\u00e0o bi\u1ec3u b\u00ec gi\u00fap da h\u1ea5p thu d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t nhanh, th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c, tr\u1ebb ho\u00e1 da.<\/li>\n<li>Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa li\u1ec7u ph\u00e1p \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng sinh h\u1ecdc di\u1ec7t khu\u1ea9n v\u00e0 m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i GSC Rebirth &amp; Recovery Mask nh\u1eb1m d\u1ecbu da nhanh ch\u00f3ng, c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m, gi\u1ea3m t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng k\u00edch \u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ecf da t\u1ee9c th\u00ec, duy tr\u00ec l\u00e0n da kho\u1ebb m\u1ea1nh.<\/li>\n<li>L\u00e0m l\u00e0nh nhanh t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da sau x\u1ea5m l\u1ea5n GSC Ultra Calming K Cream g\u1ed3m Vitamin K, chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t c\u00fac La M\u00e3 v\u00e0 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t t\u1eeb th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Th\u1eddi gian li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb 60 &#8211; 85 ph\u00fat.<\/li>\n<li>M\u1ed9t li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1eeb 01 &#8211; 03 bu\u1ed5i, kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i c\u00e1ch nhau 01 th\u00e1ng.<\/li>\n<li>V\u1edbi n\u00e1m v\u00e0 t\u0103ng s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 c\u1ea7n t\u1eeb 08 &#8211; 10 bu\u1ed5i tu\u1ef3 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng, m\u1ed7i bu\u1ed5i c\u00e1ch nhau 10 ng\u00e0y.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 0px; top: 464.224px;\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh t\u1ed1i \u01b0u d\u00e0nh cho da kh\u00f4 r\u00e1p, bong tr\u00f3c, da k\u00edch \u1ee9ng c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu.<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":3700,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"product_brand":[],"product_cat":[38],"product_tag":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-1224","1":"product","2":"type-product","3":"status-publish","4":"has-post-thumbnail","6":"product_cat-phuc-hoi","8":"first","9":"instock","10":"virtual","11":"product-type-simple"},"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product\/1224","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/product"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1224"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn